      <title>日本汽车制造商誓言加强合作以重夺中国市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/japan-s-carmakers-vow-closer-ties-to-regain-ground-lost-to-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在日本两大汽车品牌开始就一项可能将日本汽车业一分为二的协议进行谈判之际，日本最大的两家汽车制造商承诺在以技术为重点的领域进行合作，以在迅速发展的全球汽车行业中生存下来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/japan-s-carmakers-vow-closer-ties-to-regain-ground-lost-to-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
